---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Importance of Regular Exercise">
    <div class="bg-gray-100 w-5/6 mx-auto py-16 my-6 rounded-xl">
        <div class="block rounded-3xl bg-gray-900 text-white py-16">
            <header>
                <a href="../blog">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-circle-arrow-left" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 21a9 9 0 1 0 0 -18a9 9 0 0 0 0 18" /><path d="M8 12l4 4" /><path d="M8 12h8" /><path d="M12 8l-4 4" /></svg>
                </a>
                <h1>The Importance of Regular Exercise</h1>
            </header>
            
            <section>
                <h2>1. Physical Health Benefits</h2>
                <p>Regular exercise is linked to numerous physical health benefits, including improved cardiovascular health, stronger muscles, and better flexibility.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2>2. Mental and Emotional Well-being</h2>
                <p>Exercise is known to release endorphins, which can elevate mood, reduce symptoms of anxiety and depression, and contribute to overall mental well-being.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2>3. Disease Prevention</h2>
                <p>Engaging in regular physical activity is associated with a lower risk of various chronic diseases, such as diabetes, hypertension, and certain types of cancer.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2>4. Improved Sleep Quality</h2>
                <p>Consistent exercise can promote better sleep by helping regulate sleep patterns and promoting relaxation.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2>5. Enhanced Cognitive Function</h2>
                <p>Exercise has been shown to positively impact cognitive function, including improved memory, focus, and overall cognitive abilities.</p>
            </section>
            
            <footer>
                <p>Remember to incorporate a variety of exercises into your routine and consult with a healthcare professional to ensure your exercise plan aligns with your health needs.</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    div {
        padding-inline: 6rem;
        position: relative;
    }
    section {
        margin-block: 2rem;
    }
    h1 {
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #fdd308;
    }
    svg {
        position: absolute;
        top: 1em;
        left: 1em;
    }
</style>
